<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:08:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队向极端正统派男子发出数千份征兵通知，引发抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-issue-thousands-of-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-sparking-protests/00000190-bf3a-d458-a3d7-bfff171f0000</link><description>以色列军队预计将向正在犹太学院工作或已经退学的极端正统派男子发出约 6,000 份征兵通知。军队宣布这一消息后，大约 150 名来自极端极端正统教派的男子封锁了一条高速公路以示抗议</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 06:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-issue-thousands-of-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-sparking-protests/00000190-bf3a-d458-a3d7-bfff171f0000</guid></item><item><title>人权观察：至少五个巴勒斯坦组织在10月7日的袭击中犯有战争罪和反人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/human-rights-watch-at-least-five-palestinian-groups-committed-war-crimes-on-oct-7/00000190-bcfb-de8b-adfc-bdfbc1b30000</link><description>该组织的新报告反驳了哈马斯的说法，即其战斗人员被指示不要伤害儿童、妇女和老人，并指出对平民的杀害是有系统、有预谋和蓄意的</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/human-rights-watch-at-least-five-palestinian-groups-committed-war-crimes-on-oct-7/00000190-bcfb-de8b-adfc-bdfbc1b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军相信军事压力正在发挥作用，但表示哈马斯尚未被击败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-believes-military-pressure-is-paying-off-but-says-hamas-isnt-defeated-yet/00000190-bd16-d458-a3d7-bff7fb4b0000</link><description>以色列高级指挥官认为，现在与哈马斯达成协议的条件更好 ■ 与此同时，内塔尼亚胡及其政府的极右翼在谈判中没有表现出更大灵活性的迹象</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-believes-military-pressure-is-paying-off-but-says-hamas-isnt-defeated-yet/00000190-bd16-d458-a3d7-bff7fb4b0000</guid></item><item><title>尼基·黑利以以色列和伊朗为例，敦促共和党人团结起来支持特朗普</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/citing-israel-and-iran-nikki-haley-urges-republicans-to-unite-behind-trump/00000190-be6b-d2f8-abdb-be6fba2b0000</link><description>美国前驻联合国大使称赞特朗普的外交政策：“在以色列和哈马斯之间，唐纳德·特朗普很清楚谁是我们的朋友，谁是我们的敌人”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:17:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/citing-israel-and-iran-nikki-haley-urges-republicans-to-unite-behind-trump/00000190-be6b-d2f8-abdb-be6fba2b0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉威胁称，如果真主党加强对黎巴嫩平民的打击，他们将把袭击扩大到以色列更深处</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article-live/idf-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-in-latest-barrages-from-lebanon/00000190-be48-d3e0-a5fd-fffd18650000</link><description>以色列国防军：部队在加沙地带北部遭到袭击，以回应周二对斯德洛特的攻击 ■ 以色列国防军发言人向《阿拉伯报》表示：哈马斯领导人的顽固阻止我们达成协议 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，加沙已有 38,713 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，89,166 人受伤，哈马斯以色列卫生部表示 ■ 以色列国防军：真主党在最近的攻击中向以色列发射了 15 枚火箭弹；没有受伤或损坏</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 01:38:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article-live/idf-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-in-latest-barrages-from-lebanon/00000190-be48-d3e0-a5fd-fffd18650000</guid></item><item><title>当特朗普任命“美国第一”副总统时，犹太共和党高层坚称共和党是“唯一亲以色列的政党”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/top-jewish-republican-uses-gop-convention-to-make-case-for-trump-to-u-s-jews/00000190-be06-d3a7-a79e-fe57603f0000</link><description>共和党犹太联盟主席马特·布鲁克斯在共和党全国代表大会上对欢呼的人群说：“在拜登总统领导下的四年灾难性经历之后，特朗普将重建美以关系。”他告诉记者，他是共和党内部“战斗”的一部分，以“确保塔克·卡尔森党派没有立足之地”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 00:29:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/top-jewish-republican-uses-gop-convention-to-make-case-for-trump-to-u-s-jews/00000190-be06-d3a7-a79e-fe57603f0000</guid></item><item><title>监管机构猛烈抨击家庭长达数周的等待以色列社会服务部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/watchdog-slams-families-weeks-long-wait-for-israels-social-services-ministry/00000190-bcc8-de8b-adfc-bde88be50000</link><description>家庭要等待数周甚至数月才能从社会事务部机构获得帮助，认为对孩子构成风险的父母可以与他们举行监督会议，部分原因是大多数机构的工作时间少于要求的时间</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 21:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/watchdog-slams-families-weeks-long-wait-for-israels-social-services-ministry/00000190-bcc8-de8b-adfc-bde88be50000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这名以色列裔美国人质的父母在共和党大会上发言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-israeli-american-hostages-parents-are-speaking-at-gop-convention/00000190-bcd3-de8b-adfc-bdf3957b0000</link><description>奥马尔·诺伊特拉（Omer Neutra）在加沙被扣为人质已有九个多月了，他们的父母罗南·诺伊特拉（Ronen Neutra）和奥纳·诺伊特拉（Orna Neutra）说，“我们有发言权，我们将与美国人民对话，并要求他们加入我们的战斗。”两人表示，他们的讲话旨在让美国人牢记人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 19:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-israeli-american-hostages-parents-are-speaking-at-gop-convention/00000190-bcd3-de8b-adfc-bdf3957b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长报道了士兵因杀害哈马斯恐怖分子而被捕后自杀的虚假故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-minister-reports-fake-story-about-solider-committing-suicide-after-arrest/00000190-bcdb-d3a7-a79e-fedbc9270000</link><description>奥兹玛·耶胡迪特议员写道，“追捕我们英雄士兵的检察官办公室不是国家检察官办公室，而是敌人检察官办公室。”一旦发现该故事是虚假的，该帖子就被删除了</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 19:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-minister-reports-fake-story-about-solider-committing-suicide-after-arrest/00000190-bcdb-d3a7-a79e-fedbc9270000</guid></item><item><title>JD Vance 对以色列的立场如何？无论特朗普告诉他去哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-16/ty-article/.highlight/where-will-j-d-vance-stand-on-israel-wherever-trump-tells-him-to/00000190-bca4-db2d-ab90-befef57a0000</link><description>任何参与其中的人都应该问自己：当万斯无人跟随时会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 18:25:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-16/ty-article/.highlight/where-will-j-d-vance-stand-on-israel-wherever-trump-tells-him-to/00000190-bca4-db2d-ab90-befef57a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层，14,000名特工人员死伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership-14-000-operatives-killed-or-wounded/00000190-bc9c-db47-abb0-befd45310000</link><description>以军认为，哈马斯陷入人力危机，对战地武装力量的指挥控制能力正在削弱，武装分子和指挥官的动机出现“裂痕”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership-14-000-operatives-killed-or-wounded/00000190-bc9c-db47-abb0-befd45310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列盟友警告称，由于财政部长斯莫特里奇在西岸的政策，西方将针对定居活动人士实施新的制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-warn-of-new-western-sanctions-over-smotrichs-actions/00000190-bbd8-db47-abb0-bbf9bcc60000</link><description>被认为相对亲以色列的戴维·拉米本周作为英国外交大臣首次访问以色列，他在与以色列领导人的所有会晤中都提出了这个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-warn-of-new-western-sanctions-over-smotrichs-actions/00000190-bbd8-db47-abb0-bbf9bcc60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 284 天：以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-284-israeli-army-says-it-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership/00000190-bc80-d458-a3d7-bfe7f9e10000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军袭击了近东救济工程处学校，造成 15 人死亡。以色列国防军称，恐怖分子在此活动。 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：加沙南部汗尤尼斯有 17 人死亡。枪击案 ■ 以色列人因涉嫌为伊朗工作而被捕 ■ 战争进入 284 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-284-israeli-army-says-it-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership/00000190-bc80-d458-a3d7-bfe7f9e10000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯关押在加沙的以色列女兵的家人发布了被囚禁第一天的新照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-women-soldiers-held-by-hamas-release-photos-from-captivity/00000190-bc16-db47-abb0-be779d310000</link><description>照片显示，阿甘·伯杰、丹妮拉·吉尔博亚、利里·阿尔巴格、纳马·利维和卡琳娜·阿里耶夫在加沙地带的一间公寓内受伤。据军方消息人士称，这些照片是几周前在加沙地带的一次行动中发现的</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-women-soldiers-held-by-hamas-release-photos-from-captivity/00000190-bc16-db47-abb0-be779d310000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特起诉以色列人，据称该人被伊朗在网上招募从事反国家行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-to-indict-israeli-allegedly-recruited-by-iran-to-commit-acts-against-state/00000190-bbd9-d211-a5da-ffdbe2140000</link><description>21 岁的 Elimelech Stern 是以色列中部城市贝特谢梅什的居民，据称伊朗情报部门在网上联系并要求他执行悬挂横幅、藏匿金钱和运送包裹等“任务”，以换取报酬，随后被捕。加密货币支付</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-to-indict-israeli-allegedly-recruited-by-iran-to-commit-acts-against-state/00000190-bbd9-d211-a5da-ffdbe2140000</guid></item><item><title>一场巨大的欺诈使以色列数亿美元的养老金被抹去。国家什么都不做</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-huge-fraud-erased-hundreds-of-millions-of-israeli-pensions-the-state-wont-protect-them/00000190-bb65-db47-abb0-bb7556920001</link><description>资本市场管理局承认，近一年来，在其监管下的养老金中，有数亿谢克尔被盗，但没有一个受害者被告知。但接受指责是另一回事</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-huge-fraud-erased-hundreds-of-millions-of-israeli-pensions-the-state-wont-protect-them/00000190-bb65-db47-abb0-bb7556920001</guid></item><item><title>以色列公设辩护人：战时紧急立法严重侵犯囚犯权利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/public-defender-emergency-legislation-during-the-war-infringes-on-rights-of-prisoners/00000190-bb73-de8b-adfc-bb73ea3c0000</link><description>根据公设辩护人办公室 2023 年活动报告，自以色列与加沙哈马斯战争爆发以来，提起的恐怖主义煽动起诉数量比过去四年还要多，同时对警察暴行的投诉也激增</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/public-defender-emergency-legislation-during-the-war-infringes-on-rights-of-prisoners/00000190-bb73-de8b-adfc-bb73ea3c0000</guid></item><item><title>数万名阿拉伯人居住在耶路撒冷，没有自来水：“它将成为第二个加沙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-arabs-living-in-jerusalem-without-running-water-it-will-become-a-second-gaza/00000190-bb83-db81-a3f7-fb9fe9680000</link><description>耶路撒冷最大的城区缺乏自来水，似乎没有人关心：Kafr Aqab 的居民每周只能获得几个小时的水，无法洗衣服或洗地板，被迫放弃淋浴</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-arabs-living-in-jerusalem-without-running-water-it-will-become-a-second-gaza/00000190-bb83-db81-a3f7-fb9fe9680000</guid></item><item><title>位智前首席执行官：“如果我们采取正确的步骤，新加坡将像我们旁边的加沙一样”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-we-take-the-right-steps-singapore-will-look-like-gaza-next-to-us/00000190-b1bc-df47-a7bf-b1be45b20000</link><description>以色列科技界最成功的人物之一诺姆·巴丁 (Noam Bardin) 在美国工作 13 年后于 10 月 7 日后的第二天返回以色列。“这场巨大的危机为这个国家提供了一个‘重启’的机会，尽管代价高昂。” ，”他告诉《国土报》</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-we-take-the-right-steps-singapore-will-look-like-gaza-next-to-us/00000190-b1bc-df47-a7bf-b1be45b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军告诉高等法院：许多坦克在战争中受损，弹药短缺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-tells-high-court-many-tanks-damaged-in-the-war-there-is-ashortage-in-ammunition/00000190-bb29-de8b-adfc-bb298b860000</link><description>针对女兵要求被允许在战斗岗位服役的请愿书，以色列军队回复称，由于战争，将推迟将女性编入装甲部队，该计划将于 2025 年 11 月启动</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 12:15:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-tells-high-court-many-tanks-damaged-in-the-war-there-is-ashortage-in-ammunition/00000190-bb29-de8b-adfc-bb298b860000</guid></item></channel></rss>